What does this show have to offer?

- Perfect dialog (some of the best writing you could ever find) - Interesting Characters (Sherlock is pictured incredibly well - as well as the rest of the cast) - Gripping storytelling (Great cinematography and ways of advancing the story) - Clever ideas (Innovative ideas of showing what is going on inside the mind of a genius! also called Sherlock)

The show offers this and so much more apart from that. whatever you are doing right now is not relevant enough for you to NOT watch this show! first season is on Netflix GO WATCH IT!!!

10/10 - TV show history